<section class="mb4 pb2">

  <h2 class="mb1 bold">Slab Headings</h2>
  <div class="mb3">
    <p class="mb3">Caponi is BuzzFeed's slab typeface. It's default (and singular weight) is semibold. Caponi is intended to be used for News headlines only, and should never be smaller than an h5, or 0.875 rem. An h6, or anything classed with .type-6, in combination with the .slab class will default to Proxima. Headlines set in Caponi can be paired with body text set in Proxima.</p>
